snippet.title: PURPLE (game) is out!!
snippet.description:
Yes! PURPLE (game) is out TODAY!!
Android: https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=air.com.bartbonte.purple
iOS: https://apps.apple.com/app/purple-game/id6503608929

After yellow, red, black, blue, green, pink and orange, it's a new colour puzzle! Can you make the screen purple in 50 levels?
Play it, rate it and share it 💜
